Nha Trang is also home to i resort, a popular hot spring that is not too far from Hoang Dang Hotel. Hoang Dang Hotel puts the best of Nha Trang at your fingertips, making your stay both relaxing and enjoyable.

Address: 160 Ngo Gia Tu Street, Nha Trang Vietnam
